survey_response.review_text: Thank you for being so kind and patient during my appointment. Your positive attitude made the experience much more comfortable.

I like that that place very much she was perfect at her work the way she treated me did not give immediate solution in hurry but a step by step treatment and systamatic advice. She was down to earth simple and fast. The medicine she gave me was excellent though i am not a doctor but my family relations are doctors 1 dentist and others or in other field MBBS and MD but the way Dr. Shradha Das treated me systamaticly was really nice I felt homely touch. People take money or they say this this this should be done in other places and the root cause is left behind. I ask God to bless the work of her hands. I went to many places all experts but I just took her advice and just started 1 dose of medicine it was such a relef. I will surely recomand her to many who needs a dentist. I still have treatment to be undergo. Actually I wanted to thank her when I meet her next but this will be the best way. This is my experience  and like others who reads it to know and try Dr. Shradha and experience what I experience a relief and perfect a systematic treatment.  God bless all those who read this.

VEENERS ARE WONDERFUL!!
I had uneven and discolored teeth. When I visited Dental Bay for consultation, I was advised placing Veeners would be right way to go about.i am writing this feedback post all treatment as I am very pleased with the simple and not so painful procedure.My teeth are now even and I feel way more confident.Much thanks to Dr Shradha Das and her team for suggesting the right treatment and a smooth guidance during each step of the entire Veener placing process.Great work Dental Bay.Keep it up.

She did root canal and later cap … after one month the cap fell off later she said we need to do implant . I took a second opinion regarding this matter , ** ****** ****** **** **** ***** *** *** **** ******** * *** * *** ** ** *** ******* ********** ********** My mother has faced even worse experience for her root canal and wisdom tooth extraction. Which led to a cyst both the side of jaw now she has to go through a long surgery which take minimum six months to heal ** ****** *** ***** *** ** *** * ********** ****** *** *** ***** ****
Doctor is good at what She is doing. Carries out her work with finesse. I would recommend the doctor to other patients looking for dental treatment too.

Although young, Dr Shradha was very experienced *** ************** After patiently listening to my issue, she checked my teeth and explained me the issue with my molars and provided me with my options and her opinion. She also explained all the steps that will be involved with the option I chose. While performing the extraction as well while filling up the cavities, she was very gentle and took utmost care to keep the procedure as less painful as possible. All the issues were addressed in 2 sittings and I recovered completely in 3 days. Cheers!!

I had a huge gap between front two upper teeth. Dr shradha has chosen the right exact color and filled the gap in such a way that the filling looks like my very own tooth. I feel good n confident to smile now. Usually the filling chips off soon but Thanks for her advise *** ***** ********** it's been long and I still have no chipping. She is very polite and patient enough to listen all your problems and answers all doubts. She takes well care of the tooth sensations one gets during treatment. Well maintained and Very beautiful clinic. I would recommend to visit her for any dental issues. Thanks.

I am a first time dentist visitor and was this a peaceful experience for me.
Dr. Shradha was extremely patient and professional with me and my fears. She also explained each step so that I did not panic during the process .
I got a root canal done for two of my tooth. It was a pleasant experience with the staff as well who followed up the appointments and scheduled the visits.
I highly recommend them.

I went to the doctor for my RCT and CAP as well as a tooth extraction. I felt very at ease with the way the doctor explained the technicalities as well as the preventive measures. It aided me in having a painless surgery. I would recommend it to anyone who is experiencing tooth pain or needs consultation.
The doctor was patient, professional and explained the procedure well. She put me at ease and everything went seamlessly.
